ntense feeling, intellection, &amp; activity, a society of lovers &amp; wild enthusiasts....The Harmonian does not live with some 1600 people under one roof because of compulsion or altruism, but because of the sheer pleasure of all the social, sexual, economic, "gastrosophic," cultural, &amp; creative relations this association allows &amp; encourages".<a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://hermetic.com/bey/lemonade.html" id="mwB_s">"The Lemonade Ocean &amp; Modern Times A Position Paper</a> by <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Hakim_Bey" title="Hakim Bey" id="mwB_w" class="mw-redirect">Hakim Bey</a></span></li><li about="#cite_note-79" id="cite_note-79"><a href="./Socialism#cite_ref-79" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-79" class="mw-reference-text">Rougerie, Jacques, <i id="mwB_0">La Commune de Paris</i>. Paris: Presses Universitaires de France. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt208" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"978-2-13-062078-5"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwB_4"/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" about="#mwt208" id="mwB_8">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" about="#mwt208" id="mwCAA"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-2-13-062078-5" title="Special:BookSources/978-2-13-062078-5" about="#mwt208" id="mwCAE">978-2-13-062078-5</a>.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-Milza,_Pierre,_La_Commune-80" id="cite_note-Milza,_Pierre,_La_Commune-80"><span rel="mw:referencedBy"><a href="./Socialism#cite_ref-Milza,_Pierre,_La_Commune_80-0"><span class="mw-linkback-text">1 </span></a><a href="./Socialism#cite_ref-Milza,_Pierre,_La_Commune_80-1"><span class="mw-linkback-text">2 </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-M