-123" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-123" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation book" about="#mwt480" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book ","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"last":{"wt":"Gaab"},"first":{"wt":"Jeffrey S."},"url":{"wt":"https://books.google.com/books?id=-X4jgPG0360C&amp;pg=PA58"},"title":{"wt":"Munich: Hofbräuhaus &amp; History : Beer, Culture, &amp; Politics"},"publisher":{"wt":"Peter Lang"},"page":{"wt":"59"},"isbn":{"wt":"978-0-8204-8606-2"},"date":{"wt":"2006"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwCIg">Gaab, Jeffrey S. (2006). <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=-X4jgPG0360C&amp;pg=PA58" id="mwCIk"><i id="mwCIo">Munich: Hofbräuhaus &amp; History<span typeof="mw:DisplaySpace mw:Placeholder" id="mwCIs"> </span>: Beer, Culture, &amp; Politics</i></a>. Peter Lang. p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwCIw"> </span>59. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" id="mwCI0">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwCI4"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-0-8204-8606-2" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-8204-8606-2" id="mwCI8">978-0-8204-8606-2</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Munich%3A+Hofbr%C3%A4uhaus+%26+History+%3A+Beer%2C+Culture%2C+%26+Politics&amp;rft.pages=59&amp;rft.pub=Peter+Lang&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-8204-8606-2&amp;rft.aulast=Gaab&amp;rft.aufirst=Jeffrey+S.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D-X4jgPG0360C%26pg%3DPA58&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASocialism" class="Z3988" about="#mwt480" id="mwCJA"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt480" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"te