es to the Swedish Welfare State</i>. By Sven Steinmo.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-Esping-Andersen-149" id="cite_note-Esping-Andersen-149"><a href="./Socialism#cite_ref-Esping-Andersen_149-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-Esping-Andersen-149" class="mw-reference-text">Esping-Andersen, G. (1991). <i id="mwCPg">The three worlds of welfare capitalism</i>. Princeton, NJ: Princeton University Press.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-150" id="cite_note-150"><a href="./Socialism#cite_ref-150" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-150" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation book" about="#mwt715" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Cite book ","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"last":{"wt":"Weinberg"},"first":{"wt":"G.L."},"title":{"wt":"A World at Arms: A Global History of World War&amp;nbsp;II"},"isbn":{"wt":"978-0-521-55879-2"},"publisher":{"wt":"Cambridge University Press"},"page":{"wt":"264"},"year":{"wt":"1995"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwCPk">Weinberg, G.L. (1995). <i id="mwCPo">A World at Arms: A Global History of World War<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwCPs"> </span>II</i>. Cambridge University Press. p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwCPw"> </span>264. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" id="mwCP0">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwCP4"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-0-521-55879-2" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-521-55879-2" id="mwCP8">978-0-521-55879-2</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=A+World+at+Arms%3A+A+Global+History+of+World+War+II&amp;rft.pages=264&amp;rft.pub=Cambridge+University+Press&amp;rft.date=1995&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-521-55879-2&amp;rft.aulast=Weinberg&amp;rft.aufirst=