<ul id="mwCnY"><li id="mwCnc">"In short, Gorbachev aimed to lead the Soviet Union towards the Scandinavian social democratic model."</li></ul></span></li><li about="#cite_note-cia1990-209" id="cite_note-cia1990-209"><a href="./Socialism#cite_ref-cia1990_209-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-cia1990-209" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt962" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite web ","href":"./Template:Cite_web"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"http://www.umsl.edu/services/govdocs/wofact90/world12.txt"},"publisher":{"wt":"[[Central Intelligence Agency]]"},"accessdate":{"wt":"9 March 2008"},"title":{"wt":"1990 CIA World Factbook"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwCng"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.umsl.edu/services/govdocs/wofact90/world12.txt" id="mwCnk">"1990 CIA World Factbook"</a>. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Central_Intelligence_Agency" title="Central Intelligence Agency" id="mwCno">Central Intelligence Agency</a><span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwCns">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwCnw">9 March</span> 2008</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=1990+CIA+World+Factbook&amp;rft.pub=Central+Intelligence+Agency&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.umsl.edu%2Fservices%2Fgovdocs%2Fwofact90%2Fworld12.txt&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASocialism" class="Z3988" about="#mwt962" id="mwCn0"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt962" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwCn4"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-210" id="cite_note-210"><a href="./Socialism#cite_ref-210" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="