ata.pdf" id="mwDEQ">"Archived copy"</a> <span class="cs1-format" id="mwDEU">(PDF)</span>. Archived from <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.spd.de/scalableImageBlob/84620/data/20121217_progressive_alliance_abschlussstatement-data.pdf" id="mwDEY">the original</a> <span class="cs1-format" id="mwDEc">(PDF)</span> on 4 March 2014<span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwDEg">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwDEk">23 May</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Archived+copy&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.spd.de%2FscalableImageBlob%2F84620%2Fdata%2F20121217_progressive_alliance_abschlussstatement-data.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASocialism" class="Z3988" about="#mwt1267" id="mwDEo"></span><span class="cs1-maint citation-comment" about="#mwt1267" id="mwDEs">CS1 maint: Archived copy as title (<a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Category:CS1_maint:_Archived_copy_as_title" title="Category:CS1 maint: Archived copy as title" id="mwDEw">link</a>)</span><link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:CS1_maint:_Archived_copy_as_title" about="#mwt1267" id="mwDE0"/><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt1267" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwDE4"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-284" id="cite_note-284"><a href="./Socialism#cite_ref-284" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-284" class="mw-reference-text">Andrew Vincent. Modern political ideologies. Wiley-Blackwell publishing. 2010. pp. 87–88</span></li><li about="#cite_note-285" id="cite_note-285"><a href="./Socialism#cite_ref-285" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-285" class="mw-refer